---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const since = 2015;
const yearsRunning = new Date().getFullYear() - since;
---

<BaseLayout title="THE OLD MILL · 충남 아산 가족 레스토랑">
	<section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pt-20 pb-32 text-center reveal">
		<p class="text-eyebrow mb-6">Since 2015 · Asan, Korea</p>
		<h1 class="text-display mb-8">
			당신을 위한<br />행복한 시간
		</h1>
		<p class="prose-body max-w-xl mx-auto">
			충남 아산에서 {yearsRunning}년째,<br />
			가족의 중요한 순간을 함께해온 공간입니다.
		</p>
		<div class="mt-10 flex gap-3 justify-center">
			<a href="/contact" class="btn-cta">
				<span>예약 문의</span>
			</a>
			<a href="/space" class="btn-outline">
				<span>공간 둘러보기</span>
			</a>
		</div>
	</section>
	
	<!-- 히어로 풀폭 이미지 -->
	<section class="w-full mb-32">
		<div class="aspect-[16/9] md:aspect-[21/9] bg-border-warm overflow-hidden">
			<img 
				src="/images/hero/main.jpg" 
				alt="올드밀 외관 또는 메인 공간"
				class="w-full h-full object-cover"
			/>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-32">
		<h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl text-center mb-16">
			올드밀의 특별한 시간
		</h2>
		<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 reveal-stagger">
			<a href="/events/doljanchi" class="group card-hover">
				<div class="aspect-[4/5] bg-border-warm rounded-lg mb-4 overflow-hidden">
					<img 
						src="/images/events/doljanchi-cover.jpg" 
						alt="돌잔치 진행 모습"
						loading="lazy"
						class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"
	                />
				</div>
				<h3 class="font-serif text-2xl mb-2 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">돌잔치</h3>
				<p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
					아이의 첫 생일을 가족과 함께. 1층 전용홀에서 진행되는 프리미엄 돌잔치 패키지.
				</p>
			</a>

			<a href="/events/wedding" class="group">
				<div class="aspect-[4/5] bg-border-warm rounded-lg mb-4 overflow-hidden">
					<img 
						src="/images/events/wedding-cover.jpg" 
						alt="스몰웨딩 진행 모습"
						loading="lazy"
						class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"
	                />
				</div>
				<h3 class="font-serif text-2xl mb-2 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">스몰웨딩</h3>
				<p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
					1층 홀 또는 3층 A·B룸에서. 가까운 사람들과 함께하는 따뜻한 결혼식.
				</p>
			</a>

			<a href="/events/pizza-class" class="group">
				<div class="aspect-[4/5] bg-border-warm rounded-lg mb-4 overflow-hidden">
					<img 
						src="/images/events/pizza-cover.jpg" 
						alt="피자체험 진행 모습"
						loading="lazy"
						class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"
	                />
				</div>
				<h3 class="font-serif text-2xl mb-2 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">피자체험</h3>
				<p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
					아이들이 직접 만드는 화덕 피자. 단체 예약 및 생일파티 가능.
				</p>
			</a>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="bg-cta text-white reveal">
		<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 text-center">
			<h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-6">
				가까운 곳에 있습니다
			</h2>
			<p class="text-white/70 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
				충남 아산시 · 매일 11:00 - 21:30 운영<br />
				예약 문의는 전화 또는 온라인으로
			</p>
			<a href="tel:041-546-1080" class="inline-block bg-white text-cta px-8 py-3 rounded-full hover:bg-bg transition-colors">
				041-546-1080
			</a>
		</div>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>